	* text-coding.c (char_encode_shift_jis): Use
	`XCHARSET_TO_BYTE1_TABLE' for `Vcharset_latin_jisx0201' instead of
	`ucs_to_latin_jisx0201'.

	* mule-charset.c (ucs_to_latin_jisx0201): Deleted.
