	* mule-ccl.c (ccl_driver): Don't define `CCL_WriteMultibyteChar2'
	in UTF-2000 because it is not ported yet and not to use
	`FIELD2_TO_OFFICIAL_LEADING_BYTE', `MIN_LEADING_BYTE_OFFICIAL_2',
