1999-06-15  MORIOKA Tomohiko  <tomo@etl.go.jp>

	* mule.c (vars_of_mule): Provide `utf-2000' in UTF2000.

	* mule-charset.h (BUFBYTE_FIRST_BYTE_P): Modify for UTF-8 in
	UTF2000.
