	* *.[ch]: Change CONST to const globally.
	find -name '*.[ch]' | \
	xargs global-replace \
	's/(^|(?<=[^A-Za-z0-9_]))CONST((?=[^A-Za-z0-9_])|$)/const/g'
	- Remove vestigial references to CONST_IS_LOSING

