	(Fsubstitute_in_file_name):
	(Fsubstitute_insert_file_contents_internal):
	(Fwrite_region_internal):
	* emacs.c:
	* sysdep.c:
	* getloadavg.c:
	* systty.h:
	Remove vestigial APOLLO-conditional code.

